&lt;p&gt;The Learning &amp;amp; Development Specialist partners with leaders, subject matter experts, and employees across VEGA to design, implement, facilitate, and continuously improve learning and development initiatives that support business performance, employee growth, and organizational capability.&lt;/p&gt;
